column5: I am having a hard time finding a place that carries an oil filter for my F20.  Suggestions on a place in/near Brampton?  Thanks in advance
Brampton Powersports on Van Kirk might have em, I know Leisure Marine has them in Woodbridge that`s where I used to buy my yammi stuff.
leisure marine -- dont think  brampton powesports has them
If you haven't found it yet I know for sure that Advanced Small Engines in Belwood has them.  http://www.advancedsmallenginesmarine.com/
Take the Yamaha part # to your local Part source, ask them to cross refrence it to a WIX filter,  ( I wouldn't use Fram ) If you have Collins auto parts nearby, they carry that as well.
Thanks.  Picked one up at Co2 inflatables in Oakville.
